description:
While moving into my house (thanks to you guys), I've taken some time in my absence to reflect on how blessed I am from both God and you Samurai. You guys have been here for me and I haven't been here for you recently, at all. This is my final time 'returning' to YouTube. It's time to repay the favor.

Join The Samurai  http://bit.ly/1vKSGtU
